## Description {#details}

MessagePack object, represented as a tagged union of C++ types.

All types except <code><a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/msgpack/#afdae9da66bac09f4b2bfc0fd9f0559e6a4da8b7eb2c3f2007cf8238334401ef51">Type::Nil</a></code> (which has only one value, and so is completely represented by the <code>Kind</code> itself) map to a exactly one union member.

Definition at line 81 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/binaryformat/msgpackreader-h">MsgPackReader.h</a>.
